  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "chapterTitle": "跳跃式阅读和小说节选",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "913319_34_4761-4902",
          "range": "4761-4902",
          "rangeStart": 4761,
          "rangeEnd": 4902,
          "markText": "小说家总是听任自己的偏见。他所选择的题材、所塑造的人物以及对他笔下人物的态度都受自己偏见的影响。无论他写的是什么，都是对自己个性的表达，也是他的内在本能、感觉和经历的集中表现。不管他多努力去保持客观，他仍然是自身癖好的奴隶。不管他多努力想要去保持公正，他或多或少都会偏向某一方立场。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1719465653,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-27 13:20:53",
          "chapterUid": 34,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=4761&rangeEnd=4902",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=4761&rangeEnd=4902"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_33_2159-2193",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "2159-2193",
      "markText": "培养阅读的习惯能够为你筑造一座避难所，让你逃脱几乎人世间的所有悲哀。",
      "totalCount": 8080,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2159&rangeEnd=2193",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2159&rangeEnd=2193"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_33_2427-2452",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "2427-2452",
      "markText": "就我而言，同时阅读四到五本书会更符合我的阅读习惯。",
      "totalCount": 3204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2427&rangeEnd=2452",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2427&rangeEnd=2452"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_57_8191-8217",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "8191-8217",
      "markText": "生命的美别无其他，不过顺应其天性，做好分内之事罢了。",
      "totalCount": 2506,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=8191&rangeEnd=8217",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=8191&rangeEnd=8217"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_33_1355-1412",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1355-1412",
      "markText": "不管学者们对一本书的评价如何，不管他们是多么一致地对一本书盛赞，要是你对这本书不感兴趣的话，你就不必去理会这本书。",
      "totalCount": 2496,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1355&rangeEnd=1412",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1355&rangeEnd=1412"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_34_5071-5087",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "5071-5087",
      "markText": "小说家的目的不是指引，而是愉悦。",
      "totalCount": 2176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=5071&rangeEnd=5087",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=5071&rangeEnd=5087"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_33_786-885",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "786-885",
      "markText": "我接下来要提到的书籍既不会帮你拿到学位，也不会教你谋生的本事；不会教你如何航船，也不会教你如何修理停运的机器，但是这些书会让你活得更加丰满。当然，要让这些书籍起到这样的作用，你得享受地沉浸在阅读中。",
      "totalCount": 1908,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=786&rangeEnd=885",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=786&rangeEnd=885"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_37_1057-1154",
      "chapterUid": 37,
      "range": "1057-1154",
      "markText": "还有一种可能，一本书因为满足了多数人浪漫和冒险的愿望而得到畅销。毕竟在现实生活中这两种愿望是无法实现的，想要摆脱孤独与单调的生活唯一的方式便是沉溺于幻想中，如果将这种方式也禁止了，未免过于苛刻。",
      "totalCount": 1768,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=913319&chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1057&rangeEnd=1154",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/27532ae05defa7275c63f9d?chapterUid=37&rangeStart=1057&rangeEnd=1154"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "913319_33_1250-1285",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1250-1285",
      "markText": "我读完这部作品是出于责任感，当我读完最后一页的时候，心中长舒了一口气。",
